Definition: heat liberated by a unit mass of gas at its boiling point as it condenses into a liquid
Example: the heat of condensation is equal to the heat of vaporization
Synonyms: latent_heat, heat, liberated, by, a, unit, mass, of, gas, at, its, boiling, point, as, it, condenses, into, liquid, the, condensation, is, equal, to, vaporization
Category: noun.phenomenon
